},
{
  "model": "gameplay.quest",
  "pk": 4,
  "fields": {
    "name": "Plant the seeds",
    "description": "With the changing season, it's time to prepare the fields for the next crop. Planting seeds may seem simple, but the right care is needed for them to grow. Help the farm get a good start for the coming harvest.",
    "intro_text": "The air is crisp, and the soil is ready for the next growing season. You've been tasked with planting the seeds for the next harvest. While it seems like a straightforward task, it requires attention and patience. Each seed must be placed carefully in the ground, ensuring they have enough space to sprout and grow. In a few weeks, these small seeds will turn into tall, thriving crops, ready for harvest.",
    "outro_text": "With the seeds planted, you take a step back and look at the freshly prepared fields. The hard work is done for now, and all that’s left is to wait. Soon, the seeds will begin to sprout, and you'll watch them grow, knowing your efforts have laid the foundation for the village's next bountiful harvest.",
    "duration_choices": [
      300,
