{
  "model": "gameplay.quest",
  "pk": 5,
  "fields": {
    "name": "Maintain the crops",
    "description": "Crops need constant care, and it’s your job to ensure they remain healthy. Whether it’s weeding the garden or checking for pests, your attention can make all the difference in the success of the season’s yield.",
    "intro_text": "The fields are planted, but your work is far from over. The crops need your care. It's not enough to simply plant them; they must be tended to, nurtured, and protected. Weeds threaten to choke the young plants, and pests are always lurking, waiting for a chance to destroy the crops. It's time to grab your tools and head back to the fields",
    "outro_text": "The day’s labor is done, and the crops are in better shape than before. The weeds have been pulled, the pests have been dealt with, and the fields now look more vibrant. It’s a small victory, but a significant one. With your work complete, you can rest easy knowing the crops are one step closer to their full potential.",
    "duration_choices": [
