{
  "model": "gameplay.quest",
  "pk": 6,
  "fields": {
    "name": "Fertilize the land",
    "description": "Fertilizing the fields is essential for healthy crops. You must gather manure, compost, and other organic materials to ensure the soil is rich in nutrients for the next season.",
    "intro_text": "The soil needs replenishing if it’s going to produce a good harvest. The land has been worked hard, and the nutrients have been drained. It’s time to add organic matter to the fields to rejuvenate them. Whether it's spreading manure or compost, you’ll need to work the land with care to ensure it will support the crops for the season ahead.",
    "outro_text": "The land has been fertilized, and it’s ready for the next round of planting. The soil feels richer, and the promise of healthy crops feels closer than before. As you step back and admire the freshly fertilized fields, you know that the foundation has been laid for another fruitful season.",
