{
  "model": "gameplay.quest",
  "pk": 7,
  "fields": {
    "name": "Repair the barn",
    "description": "The barn is a vital part of the farm, but over time, it’s started to fall into disrepair. It’s your job to fix the roof, patch the walls, and ensure the barn is ready for the next season of harvests.",
    "intro_text": "As you walk toward the barn, you can see the signs of wear and tear. The roof leaks, the walls are cracked, and the once-sturdy structure now seems fragile. It’s time to roll up your sleeves and get to work. With the harvest season approaching, the barn must be in top condition to store all the crops you’ve worked so hard to grow.",
    "outro_text": "After hours of hard labor, the barn looks as good as new. The roof is fixed, the walls are patched, and it’s ready to store the season’s bounty. You stand back and take a deep breath, feeling a sense of accomplishment. The farm is ready for whatever the next season brings.",
